item.title: Episode 7: Colossians 3:16-4:18 | Zenovia Bernier
item.description: Paul wanted the Colossians to understand that how they lived should tell others who they were, or better yet whose they were. In this podcast, Zenovia unpacks what it means to “let the word of Christ richly dwell within you.” It should impact how we think, how we speak, and how we live—not just on Sundays in church but every day in our homes and our communities...
